text: Hey tom I will be a little late to work tomorrow as I have to take my car in for fixing. I should be there by 10am I hope. But I will leave a message on reception that you are coming, get your NDA signed while you are waiting for me so I can grab you and take you upstairs when I get in. We will have to head straight into a meeting at 10am
No problem, I’m already in London so I shouldn’t have any trouble getting there for 9.30am to get everything signed and be ready. Sounds exciting! I’ll see you in the morning :grinning:
